<% content_for :title do %>
	Web Design
<% end %>
<% content_for :meta_tags do %>
	<meta name="description" content="WebEnrich creative website designers come up with professional, innovative, SEO friendly, HTML 5 & flash based custom websites for your personal, business & corporate website needs. Outsource web & logo design and web development works to WebEnrich Vizag, Hyderabad, Bangalore India company">
	<meta name="keywords" content="Web design India, Delhi, Vizag, Bangalore, Hyderabad, website development, website design expert, SEO friendly web design consultant, logo design, outsource web design, need a website">
<% end %>
<div class="services-page">
	<div class="mobile-page-main">
		<div class="main-title">
			<div class="container">
				<h1>
					<%= link_to services_path, :class => 'left' do %>
						<%= image_tag image_path('mobile/back-arrow.png') %>
					<% end %>
					Web Design
					<a class='dropdown-button right' href='#' data-activates='dropdown1'>
						<%= image_tag image_path('mobile/options-icon-white.png') %>
					</a>
					<ul id='dropdown1' class='dropdown-content custom-drpwn-content'>
						<li>
							<%= link_to corporate_branding_path do %>
								<strong>Corporate Branding</strong>
							<% end %>
						</li>
						<li>
							<%= link_to mobile_website_design_path do %>
								<strong>Mobile Website Design</strong>
							<% end %>
						</li>
						<li>
							<%= link_to responsive_website_design_path do %>
								<strong>Responsive Website Design</strong>
							<% end %>
						</li>
						<li>
							<%= link_to website_maintenance_path do %>
								<strong>Website Maintenance</strong>
							<% end %>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</h1>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="title-content">
				<div class="services-img">
					<%= image_tag image_path('mobile/webdesign-banner-new.png') %>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="services-text">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="mob-web-design-article">
				<p>
					Welcome to the magical world of WebEnrich where businesses are transformed to look their very best, before they are ready to walk the virtual ramp. WebEnrich believes that a website not just projects your identity, but also protects it from virtual slander too.
				</p>
				<p>
					WebEnrich with its sound knowledge and experience in web design and development can make your website match up to international standards in terms of content and user friendly navigability to an extent that Bing, Yahoo and Google would welcome your website on their first pages with a red carpet.
				</p>
				<strong>Now isn’t that Wonderful?</strong>
				<%= link_to "Continue Reading", '#', :class => 'waves-effect waves-light btn hide' %>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="container">
		<div class="services-text services-inner-content">
			<div class="online-mob-web-design">
				<h2>Web Development Services offered by WebEnrich includes:</h2>
				<p>Creating a visually appealing web design: What is your strategy to stand out amidst millions of websites on the internet? Having a superior or innovative products and services helps but with so many options available in the market you have very little time to convince potential customers to spend enough time on your website to enable yourself to market your products and services.</p>
				<p>This is where our forte lies. Committed to our goal of designing innovative websites which give you that cutting edge, our team at WebEnrich enables you to market yourself better.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="online-mob-web-design">
				<h2>Search Engine Optimization (SEO) and Web Marketing:</h2>
				<p>Behind every successful man there's a woman and behind every successful website, stands an SEO friendly website design company. Right from giving your website a CSS drop down navigation and resetting your post titles to ensuring that essential SEO Wordpress plugins are installed and configured, everything that we do is to foster SEO friendliness in all aspects of your website apart from making it visually appealing.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="list-of-services list-of-detail-services">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="mob-web-services">
				<h1>Web Design Services</h1>
				<div class="card">
					<ul>
						<li>
							<%= link_to corporate_branding_path do %>
								<strong>Corporate Branding</strong>
							<% end %>
						</li>
						<li>
							<%= link_to mobile_website_design_path do %>
								<strong>Mobile Website Design</strong>
							<% end %>
						</li>
						<li>
							<%= link_to responsive_website_design_path do %>
								<strong>Responsive Website Design</strong>
							<% end %>
						</li>
						<li>
							<%= link_to website_maintenance_path do %>
								<strong>Website Maintenance</strong>
							<% end %>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<!-- Our Clients -->
	<%= render 'layouts/widgets/our_clients' %>
	<!-- start-project -->
	<%= render 'layouts/widgets/start_project' %>
</div>